    <stitle>INSTRUMENTS (Data Link Driven Instrument Cluster) - RE 200 and RE 300 - DESCRIPTION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
            <title>GENERAL</title>
            <para>All instruments are located on the instrument panel in a demountable instrument cluster (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0831401">Figure 1</hotlnk>) directly in front of the driver. Gauges and panel lights of
                the cluster are connected to the vehicle electrical system by two connectors mounted to the back side of
                the cluster.
            </para>
